summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; authorizing an easement agreement with King County, Washington, for the extension of 73rd Avenue Northeast across, under, over and upon a portion of Lot 1, Block 10, Alderwood Manor No. 14, being a portion of the City's Tolt Pipeline Right of Way in the northwest one-quarter of Section 12, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.
